#Information
info.tile.eplus.advancedEnchantmentTable=This upgraded Modification Table will allow players to control how their item is modified. The player will be given access to any modification that they have unlocked. Modifications are unlocked by using notes.
info.tile.eplus.arcaneInscriber=This block will allow players to convert modification manuals into modification notes. There is a 50% success rate, however this can be increased with modifiers, such as Obsidian, or the Eye of Ender.
info.tile.eplus.enchantmentbook=A decorative modification encyclopedia. You can dye this book using any standard dye Item. This block will also contribute towards the amount of bookshelves around a modification table. The height of the book can be increased by right clicking on it with a feather, and decreased by right clicking with an iron ingot. The ingot and feater will not be consumed.
info.item.eplus.scroll=Modification notes can be used to unlock modifications. You can find these notes in dungeon chests, or as a trade from some villagers. You can also get them as a rare drop from hostile mobs. The Arcane Inscriber can also be used to convert modification manuals into modification notes. 
info.item.eplus.tableUpgrade=The Table Upgrade can be used to convert a normal Modification Table into an Advanced Modification Table. It can be used by right clicking on the table. If that does not work, you can also craft it with the normal table. 
info.item.eplus.book=The Tome of the Empowered Guardian will give the player a special effect when used. This item is not available in normal gameplay. 

#Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.protect.all=This modification reduces damage done to the wearer from many damage sources. It stacks with modifications such as Fire Resistance and Feather Falling however it is possible to hit a limit on how much damage will be reduced. This modification can be applied to all armor types.
description.enchantment.protect.fire=This modification reduces damage taken from fire sources such as fire, blazes and lava. This modification also reduces the total amount of time the wearer will stay on fire. This modification can be applied to all armor types. 
description.enchantment.protect.fall=This modification reduces damage taken from falling, it also reduces damage taken when using ender pearls. This modification is only applicable to boots.
description.enchantment.protect.explosion=This modification reduces damage taken from explosions such as tnt or creepers. This modification also reduces the knockback from explosions. This modification can be applied to all armor types.
description.enchantment.protect.projectile=This modification reduces damage taken from projectiles such as arrows and fire charges. This modification can be applied to all armor types.
description.enchantment.oxygen=This modification improves the vision of the wearer when under water. The modification will also increase the total air of the wearer by 15 seconds per level. Time between suffocation damage is also increased by a second per level. This modification can only be applied to helmets.
description.enchantment.waterWorker=This modification improves the block breaking speed of the wearer when under water. This modification can only be applied to helmets. 
description.enchantment.thorns=This modification has a 15% chance per level to damage mobs that hurt the wearer by half a heart to two hearts. This modification can be applied to all armor types. 
description.enchantment.damage.all=This modification increases the damage of the item by 1.25 damage per level. This modification can be applied to many tool types however a sword is the primary item. 
description.enchantment.damage.undead=This modification increases damage done to undead mobs such as skeletons, zombies and the wither by 2.5 damage per level. This modification can be applied to many tools however a sword is the primary item.
description.enchantment.damage.arthropods=This modification increases damage done to "spider" based mobs such as Spiders, Cave Spiders, Silverfish and Endermites by 2.5 damage per level. This modification can be applied to many tools however swords are the primary item.
description.enchantment.knockback=This modification causes mobs hit to knocked away from the player. This modification can be applied only to swords.
description.enchantment.fire=This modification causes mobs hit to be set on fire. The mob will receive 3 points of fire damage with an additional 4 points of fire damage for every level afterwards. This modification can only be applied to swords. 
description.enchantment.lootBonus=This modification causes mobs to drop more loot. The maximum amount of loot dropped is increased by 1 per level. The chance of rare drops is increased by 3% plus an addition .5% per level afterwards. This modification can only be applied to swords.
description.enchantment.digging=This modification causes blocks to break faster by 30%/69%/120%/186%/271%. For the effect to apply the tool must be used on the correct block. This effect be applied to picks, shovels, axes and shears.
description.enchantment.untouching=This modification allows blocks that are normally not obtainable to be obtainable. Examples include ice, grass and ore blocks. This modification can be applied to picks, shovels, axes and shears.
description.enchantment.durability=This modification increases the average durability of a tool or piece of armor. This effect can be applied to almost any item in the game as long as it has durability. Examples include flint and steel, fishing rods, all armor types and tools.
description.enchantment.lootBonusDigger=This modification gives certain blocks the chance to drop twice as many items. Each level increases to the amount of chances. The odds that a chance will succeed are decreased however the drop modifier is increased. 33%/25%/20% for 2/3/4 times the drops. For blocks that drop multiple items such as melons the maximum amount of items that could be dropped is increased by 1 per level. The chance to get flint from gravel is also increased offering a 14%/25/100% chance to drop flint. This modification can be applied to picks, shovels and axes.
description.enchantment.arrowDamage=This modification increases damage done by a bow by 25% multiplied by the level + 1. Damage is rounded to the nearest half heart. This modification is only for bows.
description.enchantment.arrowKnockback=This modification will cause mobs to be knocked away from the player when hit. This modification is for bows.
description.enchantment.arrowFire=This modification will set cause arrows launched to be set on fire. Mobs hit will also be set on fire. This fire only affects mobs, players and tnt blocks. This modification is only for bows. 
description.enchantment.arrowInfinite=This modification prevents arrows from being consumed when fired. This effect requires that the player has at least one arrow in their inventory. This modification is only for bows.
description.enchantment.lootBonusFishing=This modification increases the players odds of getting treasure when fishing by 1% per level. This modification is only for fishing rods.
description.enchantment.fishingSpeed=This modification decreases the time it takes for a fish to bite the hook by 5 seconds per level. This also increases the chance to get junk and treasure by 1% per level.

#AquaCulture Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.aquacultureAppealing=This modification gives the player a greater amount of time to catch fish.
description.enchantment.aquacultureBarbedHook=This modification gives the player a better chance of catching the fish.
description.enchantment.aquacultureDoubleHook=This modification allows the player to get more than one fish or loot.
description.enchantment.aquacultureHeavyLine=This modification allows the player to catch larger and heavier fish.
description.enchantment.aquacultureLongCast=This modification allows the hook(bobber) of the fishing rod, to be casted longer.
description.enchantment.aquacultureMagnetic=This modification gives the player a greater chance to catch fish.
description.enchantment.aquacultureShortCast=This modification allows the hook(bobber) of the fishing rod, to be casted shorter.

#Artifice Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.artifice.invisible=An armour modification which makes the equipped piece of armour look invisible.
description.enchantment.artifice.soulstealing=A weapon modification that causes mobs to drop additional experience points. Higher levels causes the amount of exp to increase.
description.enchantment.artifice.resistance=An armour modification which provides protection from magical damage and wither damage. Higher levels offer better resistance.

#Thaumcraft Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.repair=Causes items to repair durability over time. This modification has two tiers, the second tier restoring durability at a faster rate. This modification can be used on weapons, Wand Foci and other tools, excluding shears.
description.enchantment.haste=Grants faster movement speed. This modification has three tiers, each increasing the speed boost given.
description.enchantment.potency=Increases the strength of a spell. This is a tier three modification, each increasing the strength of the casted spell. This modification is only applicable for Wand Foci and can have a different effect depending on what Foci is being used.
description.enchantment.frugal=Reduces the amount of vis consumed when a Wand Foci is used. This is a tier three modification, each tier granting a greater reduction. This modification is only applicable for Wand Foci.
description.enchantment.wandfortune=This modification is much like the fortune modification, allowing blocks which drop items to have a higher yield. This modification has three tiers, each increasing the chance for extra yield. This modification is only applicable for Wand Foci.

#Thaumic Tinkerer Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:slowFall=This modification will allow the wearer to fall at a slower speed and will also reduce the fall damage, however it will not negate it. This modification can be applied to boots.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:ascentBoost=This modification allows the wearer to jump considerably higher then normal. This modification can be applied on leggings.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:pounce=This modification will make the players attacks stronger while they are in the air. This modification can only be applied to leggings.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:shockwave=This modification will allow you to damage nearby entities when you fall. This effect is weakened by items which reduce your fall damage.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:autoSmelt=When applied to a tool, This modification will allow the tool to break through wooden blocks easier. This effect will make the tool take double durability against other blocks.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:tunnel=When applied to a tool, This modification will increase the digging speed when breaking blocks in a strait line.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:shatter=When applied to a tool, this tool will have a greater digging speed when breaking strong blocks.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:desintegrate=When applied to tools, this tool will break basic blocks such as dirt or stone, which the tool is suited against. Blocks which the tool will not normally break will cause double durability damage.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:vampirism=This modification can only be applied to swords. This effect will cause a portion of damage dealt to be put towards healing the user.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:dispersedStrike=This modification can only be applied to swords. This effect will cause a sword strike will have a successive strike. The successive strikes will deal less damage.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:focusedStrike=This effect can only be applied to swords. This effect will cause the damage dealt by an initial strike to be decreased, however successive strikes on the same mob will be increased.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:finalStrike=This modification can only be applied to swords. When damage is dealt, this effect gives a chance to triple the damage.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:valiance=This modification can only be applied to swords. This effect will increase the damage dealt when the holder has a lower health.
description.enchantment.ttinkerer:quickDraw=This modification is designed for bows, when applied, the time to fully draw the bow is faster.

#Ars Magica 2 Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.magicresist=Reduces amount of damage received from magical sources.
description.enchantment.soulbound=When the player dies, this item will be kept in the inventory on respawn, and will not drop on the ground.

#Red Power 2 Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.vorpal=Increases the chance that a mob will drop its head on death.
description.enchantment.disjunction=Increases damage dealt to Enderman and Wither Skeletons.

#Special Mobs Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.SpecialMobs.painBow=A bow based modification which deals additional damage which will bypass protection. Each level deals an additional half heart of damage.
description.enchantment.SpecialMobs.painSword=A sword based modification which deals additional damage which will bypass protection. Each level deals an additional half heart of damage.
description.enchantment.SpecialMobs.plagueBow=A bow based modification which gives the damaged mob a random negative effect. The possible effects are slowness, nausea, blindness, hunger, weakness and poison.
description.enchantment.SpecialMobs.plagueSword=A sword based modification which gives the damaged mob a random negative effect. The possible effects are slowness, nausea, blindness, hunger, weakness and poison.
description.enchantment.SpecialMobs.poisonBow=A bow based modification which gives the damaged mob poison. Each level increases the power of the poison effect applied.
description.enchantment.SpecialMobs.poisonSword=A sword based modification which gives the damaged mob poison. Each level increases the power of the poison effect applied.

#Natural Absorption Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.NaturalAbsorption.absorb=An modification for armour. The equipped piece of armour will increase the players maximum absorption amount.

#Simple Flight Enchantment Descriptions
description.enchantment.fly_longer=Increases the total amount of flaps on Simple Flight devices.
description.enchantment.fly_faster=Decreases the duration between flaps on Simple Flight devices. Useless on Jet Packs and Jet Gliders.

#More Swords Mod Enchantment Descriptions
description.msm.unused=Note: This item/block has been added to help achieve compatibility with other mods. As of now these do not do anything and are not an ordinary part of this mod. No new ores or tools will be added this is ONLY for for mod compatibility.
description.enchantment.msm.ignite=This modification will set damaged mobs on fire doing damage equal to that of the modification level.
description.enchantment.msm.spark=This modification will do 3 fire damage to mobs within 2.4 blocks of the damaged mob. Both the player and the target mob will not be set on fire.
description.enchantment.msm.feast=This modification will restore 0-3 durability when used. The amount restored is multiplied by the level of the effect.
description.enchantment.msm.vitality=This modification will consume 256 durability when used and in turn give the user several buffs such as regen, insta health and extra hearts.
description.enchantment.msm.venomAspect=This modification will poison target mob. The effect will last for seconds equivalent to the level of the effect. It's worth noting that many vanilla mobs such as spiders, zombies and skeletons can not be poisoned rendering this effect useless.
description.enchantment.msm.absorb=This modification has a 5% chance to restore 0-2 hunger points when used.
description.enchantment.msm.keenEdge=This modification increases the damage of the sword by 1 for each level of the effect.
description.enchantment.msm.scorn=This modification will double the damage of the sword by 2 when used in dimensions other than the surface world.
description.enchantment.msm.enderPulse=This modification will warp the player where they are looking when used. This effect has a range of 18 blocks per level. This modification will damage the item by 50 points every time it is used. The player will also take 1 damage in fall damage.
description.enchantment.msm.enderAura=This modification has a 15% chance of activating when the player is hit. When activated the player will warp to a random mob within 30 blocks. This mob may not always be friendly. If no mob is found then the effect will be canceled.
description.enchantment.msm.greed=This modification has a 7% chance to drop 1-3 extra points of exp.
description.enchantment.msm.wisdom=This modification is currently broken. My bad :/
description.enchantment.msm.frozenAspect=This modification will slow mobs for 3 seconds per level.
description.enchantment.msm.frostWave=This modification will slow mobs within 2.5 blocks of the target mob for 1.5 seconds.
description.enchantment.msm.ascension=This modification will propel targeted mobs upwards into the air. Hit the mob before it hits the ground to make increase the launch aspect of the effect exponential amount.
description.enchantment.msm.descension=This modification will cause the player to fall at a much slower rate than normal. To activate the effect press and hold shift.
description.enchantment.msm.shadows=This modification will blind the target mob for 1.5 seconds. There is also a 12% chance that the wither effect will be applied for a second.
description.enchantment.msm.decay=This modification will apply the wither effect to the target mob for just under 4 seconds.
description.enchantment.msm.stealth=This modification will cause the player to become invisible when activated. Unlike the potion of invisibility this effect will not give off particles and has no time limit or duration. To toggle this on or off simply right click with the sword. It's worth noting that swords and armor will still be visible while this effect is enabled.
description.enchantment.msm.extinction=This modification will kill all mobs on the map that are an instance of the target mob. This can be used on boats to kill all boats in the world and can be used to manage entities in the world. This effect will not target players.
